\begin{frame}[fragile]
We will add ``\textbackslash{}only'' to the plots so they show up one by one.

<<boring-plots, out.width='.5\\linewidth', fig.show='hold', fig.keep='all', fig.align='center'>>=
par(mar = c(4, 4, .1, .1))
x = rnorm(100)
hist(x, main='')
rug(x)
abline(v = mean(x), lty = 2, lwd = 3)
@
